mania}}\n|<center>'''1''' \u2013 0</center>\n|<center>2 \u2013 0</center>\n|Friendly\n|-\n|<center>21.</center>\n|2 September 2010\n|Ramat Gan Stadium, Ramat Gan, Israel\n|{{fb|Malta}}\n|<center>'''1''' \u2013 0</center>\n|<center>3 \u2013 1</center>\n|Euro 2012 qualifying\n|-\n|<center>22.</center>\n|2 September 2010\n|Ramat Gan Stadium, Ramat Gan, Israel\n|{{fb|Malta}}\n|<center>'''2''' \u2013 1</center>\n|<center>3 \u2013 1</center>\n|Euro 2012 qualifying\n|-\n|<center>23.</center>\n|2 September 2010\n|Ramat Gan Stadium, Ramat Gan, Israel\n|{{fb|Malta}}\n|<center>'''3''' \u2013 1</center>\n|<center>3 \u2013 1</center>\n|Euro 2012 qualifying\n|-\n|<center>24.</center>\n|4 June 2011\n|Skonto Stadium, Riga, Latvia\n |{{fb|Latvia}}\n|<center>0 \u2013 '''1'''</center>\n|<center>1 \u2013 2</center>\n|Euro 2012 qualifying\n|}\n\n==Career statistics==\n{{updated|13 April 2019}}<ref name = \"sbase\"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Yossi Bennayoun stats|url=http://www.bdfutbol.com/en/j/j2659.html|publisher=BDFUTBOL|accessdate=22 December 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Y. Benayoun |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/yossi-shai-benayoun/2721/ |work=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=7 September 2017}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|League Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other<ref>Includes other competitive competitions, including the [[FA Community Shield]]</ref>\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Hapoel Be'er Sheva]]\n||[[1997\u201398 Liga Leumit|1997\u201398]]\n|25||15||0||0||0||0||0||0||\u2013||\u2013||25||15\n|-\n!Total\n!25!!15!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!0!!-!!-!!25!!15\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Maccabi Haifa F.C.|Maccabi Haifa]]\n||[[1998\u201399 Liga Leumit|1998\u201399]]\n|29||16||3||2||3||2||7||2||\u2013||\u2013||42||24\n|-\n||[[1