FA Europa League winning players]]\n[[Category:Israel under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Israel international footballers]]\n[[Category:FIFA Century Club]]\n[[Category:Israeli expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Israeli expatriate sportspeople in the Netherlands]]\n[[Category:Israeli expatriate sportspeople in Spain]]\n[[Category:Israeli expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in the Netherlands]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Spain]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n", "name_user": "2a00:23c8:5500:7f01:1581:7823:de1d:41ff", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Changes to goal numbers)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yossi_Benayoun"}
{"title_page": "Singularity (Lead album)", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Singularity\n| type       = Studio\n| artist     = [[Lead (band)|Lead]]\n| cover      = Lead_-_Singularity.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = March 18, 2020\n| recorded   = 2019-2020\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Hip hop music|Hip-hop]], [[pop music|pop]], [[R&B]], [[dance music|dance]]\n| length     =\n| label      = [[Pony Canyon]]<br><small>CD (PCCA-4903)<br/>CD+DVD (PCCA-04901)<br/>2CD+Booklet (PCCA-04902)</small>\n| producer   =\n| prev_title = [[Milestone (Lead album)|Milestone]]\n| prev_year  = 2018\n| next_title = \n| next_year  = \n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Singularity\n | type        = studio\n | single1     = [[Be the Naked]]\n | single1date = January 30, 2019\n | single2     = [[Summer Vacation (song)|Summer Vacation]]\n | single2date = July 24, 2019\n | single3     = [[Hide and Seek/Sunset Refrain]]\n | single3date = February 17, 2020\n}}\n}}\n\n'''''Singularity''''' (stylized as ''SINGULARITY'') is the ninth [[studio album]] released by the [[Japan]]ese [[hip-hop]] group [[Lead (band)|Lead]], released on March 18, 2020, nearly two years after their previous album, ''[[Milestone (Lead album)|Milestone]]''. It debuted at No. 12 on the [[Oricon]] charts, becoming their first in eight years not to debut in the top ten.\n\nThe album included their singles ''[[Be the Naked]], [[Summer Vacation (song)|Summer Vacation]]'' and ''[[Hide and Seek/Sunset Refrain]].''\n\n''Singularity'' was released in three separate editions; a CD only version, a 2CD edition that contained a special booklet, and a CD+DVD edition, which housed music videos for not only the videos from the singles, but the previously unreleased video for \"Hide and Seek\".\n\n==Information==\n''Singularity'' is the ninth [[studio album]] released by the Japanese hip-hop [[dance troupe|group]] [[Lead (band)|Lead]], released two years after their previous studio album ''[[Milestone (Lead album)|Milestone]]''. The album debuted on the [[Oricon Albums Chart]]s at No. 12, breaking their string of top ten album releases, which began in 2012 with their studio album ''[[Now or Never (Lead album)|Now or Never]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/d/2020-03-17/p/2/|title=\u30c7\u30a4\u30ea\u30fc\u3000\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b02020\u5e7403\u670817\u65e5\u4ed8|work=[[Oricon]]|accessdate=March 19, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/304509/rank/album/|title=Lead\u306e\u58f2\u4e0a\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0|work=Oricon|accessdate=March 19, 2020}}</ref> By the second day, it had dropped to the No. 20 spot.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/d/2020-03-18/p/2/|title=\u30c7\u30a4\u30ea\u30fc\u3000\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b02020\u5e7403\u670818\u65e5\u4ed8|work=Oricon|accessdate=March 19, 2020}}</ref>\n\nThe album was released in three separate editions: a standard [[compact disc|CD]] containing thirteen musical tracks;<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yesasia.com/us/singularity-normal-edition-japan-version/1087123683-0-0-0-en/info.html|title=SINGULARITY (Normal Edition)(Japan Version)|work=[[YesAsia]]|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}</ref> a type A CD+[[DVD]] edition, which housed music videos for all the videos from the singles, along with the previously unreleased \"Hide and Seek\";<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yesasia.com/us/singularity-type-a-album-dvd-first-press-limited-edition-japan-version/1087123677-0-0-0-en/info.html|title=SINGULARITY [Type A](ALBUM+DVD)(First Press Limited Edition)(Japan Version)|work=YesAsia|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}</ref> and a type B 2CD edition that contained thirteen tracks on the first disc, a special radio show hosted by the group, a remix of \"Summer Vacation\", a live version of \"[[Beautiful Day (Lead song)|Say Good-bye Say Hello]]\" and a special booklet.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yesasia.com/us/singularity-type-b-album-booklet-first-press-limited-edition-japan/1087123681-0-0-0-en/info.html|title=SINGULARITY [Type B](ALBUM+BOOKLET)(First Press Limited Edition)(Japan Version)|work=YesAsia|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}</ref> All editions were also given first press limited editions, which included tickets to the group's upcoming live event, ''Leaders Party 17! ~Breakthrough~''.\n\nAs a special promotion, when buyers pre-ordered the album at various CD shops nationwide, they could receive a clear file folder. The company also collaborated with [[Amazon (company)|Amazon Japan]] for several promotions, including a DECA jacket with the pattern of either the A or B special edition.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%80%90Amazon-co-jp%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%91SINGULARITY-%E5%88%9D%E5%9B%9E%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E7%9B%A4B-2CD-%E3%82%B9%E3%83%9A%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A3%E3%83%AB%E3%83%96%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AC%E3%83%83%E3%83%88-%E3%83%87%E3%82%AB%E3%82%B8%E3%83%A3%E3%82%B1%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%E4%BB%98/dp/B083Q8N6QY/ref=pd_sim_15_1/356-3959280-0312829?_encoding=UTF8&pd_rd_i=B083Q8N6QY&pd_rd_r=8a9796d7-4dbf-402b-9ef3-b0552ff698af&pd_rd_w=KqeKs&pd_rd_wg=eYzdu&pf_rd_p=17855d03-fe8b-4da2-b202-665b81270246&pf_rd_r=X27CCJRXPFS83G9MF6W7&psc=1&refRID=X27CCJRXPFS83G9MF6W7|title=\u3010Amazon.co.jp\u9650\u5b9a\u3011SINGULARITY \u521d\u56de\u9650\u5b9a\u76e4B [2CD+\u30b9\u30da\u30b7\u30e3\u30eb\u30d6\u30c3\u30af\u30ec\u30c3\u30c8](\u30c7\u30ab\u30b8\u30e3\u30b1\u30c3\u30c8\u4ed8)|work=[[Amazon Japan]]|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%80%90Amazon-co-jp%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%91SINGULARITY-%E5%88%9D%E5%9B%9E%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E7%9B%A4A-CD-DVD-%E3%83%87%E3%82%AB%E3%82%B8%E3%83%A3%E3%82%B1%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%E4%BB%98/dp/B083Q8CVVK/ref=sr_1_3?__mk_ja_JP=%E3%82%AB%E3%82%BF%E3%82%AB%E3%83%8A&crid=2FH3VAZSI67NJ&dchild=1&keywords=lead+singularity&qid=1584362627&s=music&sprefix=lead+singu%2Cpopular%2C300&sr=1-3-catcorr|title=\u3010Amazon.co.jp\u9650\u5b9a\u3011SINGULARITY \u521d\u56de\u9650\u5b9a\u76e4A [CD+DVD](\u30c7\u30ab\u30b8\u30e3\u30b1\u30c3\u30c8\u4ed8) CD+DVD|work=Amazon Japan|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}</ref> At each venue for their fan club tour ''Leaders Party 17! ~Breakthrough~'' <small>(stylized as ''Leaders Party 17! ~BREAKTHROUGH~'')</small>, which will be held in April 2020, those who purchase a CD, DVD or [[Blu-ray]] will receive a ''Singularity''-themed poster.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lead.tv/news/5431/|title=\u3010\u4e88\u7d04\u7279\u5178\u7d75\u67c4\u516c\u958b\u3011\u901a\u7b979\u4f5c\u76ee\u3068\u306a\u308b\u30aa\u30ea\u30b8\u30ca\u30eb\u30fb\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u300cSINGULARITY\u300d3/18\u767a\u58f2\u6c7a\u5b9a\uff01|work=Lead Official|date=February 18, 2020|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Promotional activities==\nPrior to the album's release, the group had released three singles: ''Be the Naked'', ''Summer Vacation'' and ''Hide and Seek/Sunset Refrain''.\n\n''[[Be the Naked]]'' was the thirtieth single released by Lead, and was their first single of 2019. It debuted in the top ten on the Oricon Singles Charts at No. 7 and climbed to the No. 6 spot by the third day.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/js/d/2019-01-29/|title=\u30aa\u30ea\u30b3\u30f3\u30c7\u30a4\u30ea\u30fc\u3000\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b02019\u5e7401\u670829\u65e5\u4ed8|work=[[Oricon]]|date=January 29, 2019|accessdate=January 30, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/js/d/2019-01-31/|title=\u30aa\u30ea\u30b3\u30f3\u30c7\u30a4\u30ea\u30fc\u3000\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b02019\u5e7401\u670831\u65e5\u4ed8|work=[[Oricon]]|date=January 29, 2019|accessdate=February 2, 2019}}</ref> It was released in four formats: a standard CD, two CD+DVD editions, and a CD+booklet edition. The CD only version housed the title track and two coupling tracks, while the other editions carried the title track and one of two coupling tracks. ''[[Summer Vacation (song)|Summer Vacation]]'' was their thirty-fifth single and debuted at No. 6 on the [[Oricon Singles Chart]]s, becoming their fourteenth consecutive single to chart in the top ten.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/js/d/2019-07-23/|title=\u30c7\u30a4\u30ea\u30fc\u3000\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 2019\u5e7407\u670823\u65e5\u4ed8|work=[[Oricon]]|date=July 23, 2019|accessdate=July 24, 2019}}</ref> It came in four formats: a standard [[compact disc|CD]], two CD+DVD editions, and a CD+booklet edition. The CD only version carried three songs: the title track \"Summer Vacation\", and the two [[b-side|coupling tracks]] \"Paradise City\" and \"Anthem\".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/PCCA-4803?s_ssid=e325b85d12f3517227|title=Summer Vacation [Regular Edition]|work=CDJapan|accessdate=June 26, 2018}}</ref> As with their previous single, each edition harbored the main track and one of two b-sides. \n\n''[[Hide and Seek/Sunset Refrain]]'' was their thirty-second single, and final single before their album ''Singularity''. The single continued their streak of top-charting singles, and peaked at No. 3 on the [[Oricon Singles Chart]]s.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/js/w/2020-03-02/|title=\u9031\u9593\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b02020\u5e7403\u670802\u65e5\u4ed8\uff082020\u5e7402\u670817\u65e5\uff5e2020\u5e7402\u670823\u65e5\uff09|work=[[Oricon]]|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref> The single was released in four formats: a standard CD, two CD+DVD editions, and a CD+booklet edition. The standard CD housed the title tracks and the [[b-side|coupling track]] \"Midnight Free Way\",<ref>{{cite web|url=https://item.rakuten.co.jp/hmvjapan/10355712/|title=\u30ea\u30fc\u30c9 / HIDE and SEEK / \u30b5\u30f3\u30bb\u30c3\u30c8\u30fb\u30ea\u30d5\u30ec\u30a4\u30f3 - \u697d\u5929\u5e02\u5834|work=Rakuten|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref> while the CD+DVD editions only contained the two a-sides.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://item.rakuten.co.jp/hmvjapan/10355709/|title=Lead (JP) \u30ea\u30fc\u30c9 / H I D E and S E E K / \u30b5\u30f3\u30bb\u30c3\u30c8\u30fb\u30ea\u30d5\u30ec\u30a4\u30f3 \u3010\u521d\u56de\u9650\u5b9a\u76e4A\u3011 \u3010CD Maxi\u3011|work=Rakuten|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://item.rakuten.co.jp/hmvjapan/10355710/|title=Lead (JP) \u30ea\u30fc\u30c9 / H I D E and S E E K / \u30b5\u30f3\u30bb\u30c3\u30c8\u30fb\u30ea\u30d5\u30ec\u30a4\u30f3 \u3010\u521d\u56de\u9650\u5b9a\u76e4B\u3011 \u3010CD Maxi\u3011|work=Rakuten|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref> The CD+booklet, however, featured the two title tracks, along with their corresponding instrumentals.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://item.rakuten.co.jp/hmvjapan/10355711/|title=Lead (JP) \u30ea\u30fc\u30c9 / H I D E and S E E K / \u30b5\u30f3\u30bb\u30c3\u30c8\u30fb\u30ea\u30d5\u30ec\u30a4\u30f3 \u3010\u521d\u56de\u9650\u5b9a\u76e4C\u3011(+\u30b9\u30da\u30b7\u30e3\u30eb\u30d6\u30c3\u30af\u30ec\u30c3\u30c8) \u3010CD Maxi\u3011|work=Rakuten|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref>\n\nAs a special promotion, when buyers pre-ordered the album at various CD shops nationwide, they could receive a clear file folder. The company also collaborated with Amazon Japan where buyers would receive a DECA jacket with the pattern of either the A or B special edition cover. At each venue for their fan club tour ''Leaders Party 17! ~Breakthrough~'', which will be held in April 2020, those who purchase a music CD or DVD/Blu-ray will receive a ''Singularity''-themed poster.\n\nIn an effort to aid in promotion, on March 22, a live broadcast was launched on ''LINE LIVE'', where the group talked about the album.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lead.tv/news/5564/|title=3/22(\u65e5) \u300cSINGULARITY\u300d\u767a\u58f2\u8a18\u5ff5\u751f\u653e\u9001 #\u5148\u5c0e\u7684\u7279\u7570\u70b9 LINE LIVE\u914d\u4fe1\u6c7a\u5b9a\uff01|work=LINE|accessdate=March 25, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{