ny Canyon]] put out a notice that several of the scheduled live events had been postponed or cancelled due to the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]]. All events between March 18 and March 22 were cancelled indefinitely.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ameblo.jp/lead-blog/entry-12576790697.html|title=\u3010\u30b9\u30bf\u30c3\u30d5\u3088\u308a\u30112\u670822\u65e5\uff5e3\u670822\u65e5CD\u767a\u58f2\u8a18\u5ff5\u30a4\u30d9\u30f3\u30c8\u306e\u958b\u50ac\u4e2d\u6b62\u304a\u3088\u3073\u5ef6\u671f\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b|work=Ameba|date=February 21, 2020|accessdate=March 17, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Charts (Japan)==\n===Album===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!align=\"left\"|Release\n!align=\"left\"|Chart\n!align=\"left\"|Peak position\n!align=\"left\"|Chart run\n!align=\"left\"|Total sales\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|March 18, 2020\n|align=\"left\"|[[Billboard Japan]]\n|align=\"center\"|15\n|align=\"center\"|\n|align=\"center\"|5,855<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard-japan.com/charts/detail?a=top_albums&year=2020&month=03&day=30|title=Billboard Japan Top Albums Sales / Charts / Billboard JAPAN|work=[[Billboard Japan]]|accessdate=April 3, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!align=\"left\"|Release\n!align=\"left\"|Chart\n!align=\"left\"|Peak position\n!align=\"left\"|Chart run\n!align=\"left\"|Total sales\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|March 18, 2020\n|align=\"left\"|[[Oricon|Oricon Daily Albums Chart]]\n|align=\"center\"|12\n|align=\"center\"|\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|March 18, 2020\n|align=\"left\"|[[Oricon Albums Chart|Oricon Weekly Albums Chart]]\n|align=\"center\"|17\n|align=\"center\"|\n|align=\"center\"|5,196<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2020-03-30/|script-title=ja:\u9031\u9593 CD\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 2020\u5e7403\u670830\u65e5\u4ed8|trans-title=Weekly CD Album Ranking on March 30, 2020|publisher=Oricon|accessdate=March 25, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|March 18, 2020\n|align=\"left\"|