ri/actualitate/5-cazuri-de-coronavirus-confirmate-in-romania-1270242|title=6 cazuri de coronavirus confirmate \u00een Rom\u00e2nia. 2 pacien\u021bi testa\u021bi pozitiv ast\u0103zi|website=Digi24|date=4 March 2020|access-date=4 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200309191018/https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/5-cazuri-de-coronavirus-confirmate-in-romania-1270242|archive-date=9 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! 6\n| {{Failure|Hospitalised}}\n| Imported case\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Suceava County|Suceava]]\n| Male\n| 71\n| Moved to intensive care on 18 March; comorbid lymphoma.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ziaruldeiasi.ro/stiri/covid-19-la-iasi-primele-probleme-grave-doi-pacienti-la-ati-lipsuri-materiale-in-spitale--247192.html|website=Ziarul de Iasi|date=19 March 2020|title=COVID-19 la Ia\u015fi: primele probleme grave. Doi pacien\u021bi la ATI, lipsuri materiale \u00een spitale}}</ref>\n|-\n! 7\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 6 Mar.\n| {{Success|Recovered}}<ref name=\"tion\" />\n| Local transmission\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Timi\u0219 County|Timi\u0219]]\n| Female\n| 16\n| Classmate of case #5.\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-23703735-ultima-ora-tanara-16-ani-din-timisoara-saptelea-caz-confirmat-coronavirus.htm|title=O t\u00e2n\u0103r\u0103 de 16 ani din Timi\u0219oara, al \u0219aptelea caz confirmat cu coronavirus|website=HotNews.ro|author=J., S.|date=6 March 2020|access-date=11 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306160813/https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-23703735-ultima-ora-tanara-16-ani-din-timisoara-saptelea-caz-confirmat-coronavirus.htm|archive-date=6 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! 8\n| {{Failure|Hospitalised}}\n| Imported case\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Olt County|Olt]]\n| Male\n| 51\n| He travelled on the same coach with case #6.\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-sanatate-23704639-8-lea-caz-infectie-coronavirus-confirmat-romania-femeie-51-ani-din-olt-care-intors-din-italia.htm|title=Al 8-lea caz de infec\u021bie cu coronavirus, confirmat \u00een Olt: Un b\u0103rbat de 51 de ani care s-a \u00eentors din Italia|website=HotNews.ro|author=Neagu, Alina|date=6 March 2020|access-date=6 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307161732/https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-sanatate-23704639-8-lea-caz-infectie-coronavirus-confirmat-romania-femeie-51-ani-din-olt-care-intors-din-italia.htm|archive-date=7 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! 9\n| {{Success|Recovered}}<ref name=\"recovered-14-mar\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ms.ro/2020/03/14/proceduri-de-externare-pentru-3-pacienti-internati-la-spitalul-de-boli-infectioase-timisoara|title=Proceduri de externare pentru 3 pacien\u021bi interna\u021bi la Spitalul de Boli Infec\u021bioase Timi\u0219oara|language=ro|website=Ministerul S\u0103n\u0103t\u0103\u021bii|date=14 March 2020|access-date=14 March 2020}}</ref>\n| Imported case\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Hunedoara County|Hunedoara]]\n| Male\n| 44\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/al-optulea-caz-de-coronavirus-confirmat-in-romania-1271262|title=Alte dou\u0103 cazuri de coronavirus confirmate vineri, \u00een Rom\u00e2nia. Noul bilan\u021b: 9 pacien\u021bi infecta\u021bi cu COVID-19 |website=Digi24|date=6 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! 10\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 7 Mar.\n| {{Success|Recovered}}<ref name=\"tion\" /><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.news.ro/social/doi-pacienti-internati-cu-coronavirus-in-timisoara-s-au-vindecat-si-vor-fi-externati-1922401210172020032019298449 |title=Doi pacien\u021bi interna\u021bi cu coronavirus \u00een Timi\u0219oara s-au vindecat \u0219i vor fi externa\u021bi |website=News.ro |author=Iedu, Liliana |date=10 March 2020}}</ref>\n| Local transmission\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Timi\u0219 County|Timi\u0219]]\n| Female\n| 15\n| She is studying at the same high school with cases #5 and #7, but not in the same class.\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-23706416-alte-doua-cazuri-c